data.description: You'll fall in love with this amazing updated bungalow located on a quiet street in an area of charming homes.  Filled with character including natural woodwork, multiple built-ins, and is combined with fantastic seamless updates including an incredible kitchen with a cathedral ceiling, raised split breakfast/snack bar, dual ovens, built-in gas range and much more!  Incredible owner suite has updated bathroom with jetted tub and huge walk-in ceramic tiled shower.  Rear deck overlooks private fenced-in backyard.  Awesome flexible floor plan with private den that could also function as a 4th bedroom.  Hurry, this amazing find won't be around long!
